(6553,'The Datetime module provides a Date field that stores dates and times. It also provides the Form API elements <em>datetime</em> and <em>datelist</em> for use in programming modules. See the <a href=\":field\">Field module help</a> and the <a href=\":field_ui\">Field UI module help</a> pages for general information on fields and how to create and manage them. For more information, see the <a href=\":datetime_do\">online documentation for the Datetime module</a>.','','none'),
