(6555,'Dates can be displayed using the <em>Plain</em> or the <em>Default</em> formatter. The <em>Plain</em> formatter displays the date in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601\">ISO 8601</a> format. If you choose the <em>Default</em> formatter, you can choose a format from a predefined list that can be managed on the <a href=\":date_format_list\">Date and time formats</a> page.','','none'),
