(8908,'Drupal is an open source platform for building amazing digital experiences. It’s made, used, taught, documented, and marketed by the <a href=\"@drupal_community\">Drupal community</a>. Our community is made up of people from around the world with a shared set of <a href=\"@drupal_values\">values</a>, collaborating together in a respectful manner. As we like to say:','','none'),
